<title>UK: BZW sets warrants on basket of European data firms.</title>
<headline>BZW sets warrants on basket of European data firms.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-10-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>BZW Warrants has issued one million American-style call warrants on a basket of European data firms. The firms included are Cap Gemini, Sligos, CMG, Logica, SAP, Getronics and Baan Company, lead manager BZW Securities said.</p>
<p>One basket is controlled by 100 warrants</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    10000 STG		 ISSUE PRICE  21.10 STG</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	09.OCT.98		 LISTING	LUX</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE  10000 STG		 MIN EXER LOT 100</p>
<p>-- Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
